  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-119fve5\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"2SNeVD_e\"><span class=\"highlight-wrap other\" data-highlight-id=\"1924171587055257440\" data-highlight-split-type=\"head\" data-highlight-id-extra=\"\">男性的</span><span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=731747858&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E7%9D%BE%E9%85%AE%E7%B4%A0&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"highlight-wrap other\" data-highlight-id=\"1924171587055257440\" data-highlight-split-type=\"none\" data-highlight-id-extra=\"\">睾酮素</span><svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span><span class=\"highlight-wrap other has-comments\" data-highlight-id=\"1924171587055257440\" data-highlight-split-type=\"tail\" data-highlight-id-extra=\"\">是女性的20-25倍，一个普通男性就相当于女性里的性瘾患者</span></p><p data-pid=\"7a7kZr9S\">男人，或者说自然界中大部分雄性。</p><p data-pid=\"6YD2Zx0y\">一级需求不是吃饭，不是生存，不是玩乐</p><p data-pid=\"Lvk6uXiS\"><span class=\"highlight-wrap other\" data-highlight-id=\"1923389421522257281\" data-highlight-split-type=\"both\" data-highlight-id-extra=\"\">而是连接。想要连接。</span></p><p data-pid=\"P7_1mC--\"><span class=\"highlight-wrap other\" data-highlight-id=\"1922729513751680108\" data-highlight-split-type=\"head\" data-highlight-id-extra=\"\">就算不是为了具体的自己的连接也是会为了抽象的</span><span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\