23369148748129060,1992213545824301983\" data-highlight-split-type=\"both\" data-highlight-id-extra=\"\">不是人长了牛子，</span></p><p data-pid=\"0ptan919\"><span class=\"highlight-wrap other\" data-highlight-id=\"1921840805162771583,1921840826276877243,1923369148748129060,1992213545824301983\" data-highlight-split-type=\"both\" data-highlight-id-extra=\"\">而是牛子需要连接，所以长出了人。</span></p><p data-pid=\"jV5GMkXl\">很多左派立大旗说人不交配不会死，性与爱不是刚需。但问题是生物的生存本来就是繁衍的刚需。</p><p data-pid=\"YiFoRdvk\">只能说在<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=731747858&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E7%BB%8F%E4%B9%A6&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">经书<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>的影响下把人的精神太神圣化了，这也是左派总是失败的原因。</p></span><span id=\"VirtualCatalogAnchorPoint\"></span></span></div>",
